39
00:03:14,220 --> 00:03:18,339
I don't want to doubt anyone, but you can't always rely on your gut feeling.

40
00:03:18,339 --> 00:03:20,820
Should I go with the safe data from Mr. Liu and wait for defeat?

41
00:03:20,820 --> 00:03:24,240
Then why didn't you tell Miss Mofei about this?

42
00:03:25,140 --> 00:03:28,040
Her prejudice against Shen Xi is too deep,
so it's no use talking about it.

43
00:03:28,040 --> 00:03:31,219
I'm not just going with my gut feeling here. 
I've tested out Shen Xi's adjustments to the car,

44
00:03:31,219 --> 00:03:33,960
and it's completely different from Mr. Liu's.

45
00:03:35,360 --> 00:03:37,460
Achieve great success in one fell swoop.

46
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:41,120
Why don't I help her break all of her restraints?

47
00:03:41,639 --> 00:03:44,000
She always gets stuck in her own traps.

48
00:03:44,420 --> 00:03:48,264
This time, I'm going to tell her

49
00:03:49,259 --> 00:03:50,640
that she's worth trusting,

50
