54
00:04:19,700 --> 00:04:22,480
Your words have me

55
00:04:22,920 --> 00:04:24,800
fired up!

56
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:26,940
Alright, what else is there to say?

57
00:04:26,940 --> 00:04:29,019
- Let's do it.
- Let's go.

58
00:04:29,019 --> 00:04:32,959
By the way, the issue of using Shen Xi's data

59
00:04:32,959 --> 00:04:34,848
must be kept secret to the outside.

60
00:04:34,848 --> 00:04:36,172
Ok.

61
00:04:49,348 --> 00:04:54,052
[Even if the whole world doesn't believe you]

62
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:16,304
Mobai,

63
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:18,580
are there any issues?

64
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:20,480
You don't trust me?

65
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:22,659
It's not that, just in case…

66
00:05:23,620 --> 00:05:25,940
What if it rains? What should we do then?

67
00:05:25,940 --> 00:05:27,800
Why don't we reschedule it?

68
00:05:27,800 --> 00:05:30,420
I've already notified everyone. Reporters are coming today.

69
00:05:30,420 --> 00:05:32,459
Even if it rains acid, we have to do it.

70
00:05:32,459 --> 00:05:34,959
Why don't we replace the rain tires in advance?

71
00:05:34,959 --> 00:05:37,279
This way, although the speed is slower, it would be a lot safer.

72
00:05:37,279 --> 00:05:39,660
When did you become such a fusspot?

73
00:05:39,660 --> 00:05:41,980
The bystander is more concerned than the person concerned

74
00:05:41,980 --> 00:05:45,056
Xu Gong, give me at the scene later.

75
00:05:45,056 --> 00:05:47,559
Mobai, where are you going?

76
00:05:47,559 --> 00:05:49,572
It's about to start.

77
00:05:50,100 --> 00:05:52,520
What did I do wrong?

78
00:05:52,520 --> 00:05:56,720
I can't watch Mr. Mobai test the car. I have to work overtime here.

79
00:06:00,759 --> 00:06:02,792
I'm sorry.

80
00:06:11,519 --> 00:06:13,508
Mr. Mobai,

81
00:06:14,100 --> 00:06:16,204
are you free today?

82
00:06:16,204 --> 00:06:17,880
Me?

83
00:06:17,880 --> 00:06:19,240
Yes.

84
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:22,939
Would you mind finishing Shen Xi's record today?

85
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:27,944
Come with me.

86
00:06:39,659 --> 00:06:41,900
Even though this is quite important,

87
00:06:41,900 --> 00:06:44,040
