88
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:46,679
It looks like Mr. Mobai is pretty confident.

89
00:06:46,679 --> 00:06:50,640
To save his few people, he must have put in a lot of effort.

90
00:06:50,640 --> 00:06:54,339
It sounds like Mr. An doesn't really want Chen Mobai to win.

91
00:06:54,879 --> 00:06:58,380
On this point, I'm with Miss Zhao.

92
00:06:58,380 --> 00:07:02,800
Professional matters should be left to professionals.

93
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:06,639
His rag-tag team should be replaced.

94
00:07:10,380 --> 00:07:12,600
Are you worried about rain?

95
00:07:13,759 --> 00:07:15,816
Murphy's Law.

96
00:07:16,519 --> 00:07:19,460
This time, he's not just doing it for himself but for everyone.

97
00:07:19,460 --> 00:07:23,460
So he will give it his all. Don't worry.

98
00:07:24,319 --> 00:07:25,976
What?

99
00:07:26,839 --> 00:07:29,399
Does Miss Mofei lack confidence today?

100
00:07:29,399 --> 00:07:33,600
It depends. I believe in Chen Mobai's ability

101
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:36,460
but after all, but he's recently recovered from a big injury,

102
00:07:36,460 --> 00:07:39,600
