112
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:15,379
This is certainly not what you want.

113
00:08:15,379 --> 00:08:16,884
So…

114
00:08:17,540 --> 00:08:21,679
You hope to lose this bet more than I do,

115
00:08:21,679 --> 00:08:23,920
