181
00:13:30,420 --> 00:13:33,480
I'll explain to you later. We used other data this time.

182
00:13:33,480 --> 00:13:35,459
What's going on?

183
00:13:35,459 --> 00:13:39,620
Miss Mofei, the team's debugging data is different
from mine.

184
00:13:39,620 --> 00:13:41,959
It seems to be another one.

185
00:13:45,600 --> 00:13:48,360
