215
00:17:15,860 --> 00:17:18,599
- Mobai is really something. 
 - Do you know how fast you were?

216
00:17:18,599 --> 00:17:20,480
- Chubby, you tell him.
- One minute thirty seconds nine-nine-seven.

217
00:17:20,480 --> 00:17:23,260
You broke Mitsui's record in an instant.

218
00:17:25,056 --> 00:17:26,100
Bad news.

219
00:17:26,100 --> 00:17:28,280
If there's anything else,
we'll talk about it later. Where's Shen Xi?

220
00:17:28,280 --> 00:17:32,080
It's about Shen Xi and Miss Mofei.

221
00:17:32,080 --> 00:17:34,016
What happened?

222
00:17:34,039 --> 00:17:37,259
Miss Mofei slapped Shen Xi.

223
00:17:37,259 --> 00:17:40,320
I'm afraid she might have an accident
because she doesn't seem alright.

224
00:17:40,320 --> 00:17:42,919
- Where is she now? 
 - She's gone.

225
00:17:42,920 --> 00:17:46,500
Don't think that just because I let you race, you can do whatever you want.

226
00:17:59,759 --> 00:18:01,499
Go and get him back quickly.

227
00:18:01,519 --> 00:18:02,960
Here.

228
00:18:05,640 --> 00:18:07,356
Jiang Wei.

229
00:18:08,659 --> 00:18:10,900
Don't worry. Leave it to me.

230
00:18:15,620 --> 00:18:16,740
[Duanmu Kuan]

231
00:18:17,960 --> 00:18:19,876
Hello, Mr. Kuan.

232
00:18:22,359 --> 00:18:24,256
Are you sure?

233
00:18:26,219 --> 00:18:28,419
I'll be right at the lab.

234
00:18:34,759 --> 00:18:37,840
Miss Zhao, I'm really sorry.

235
00:18:37,840 --> 00:18:40,739
There were a few small mistakes
in our management.

236
00:18:40,739 --> 00:18:42,160
We will definitely strengthen our management
in the future.

237
00:18:42,160 --> 00:18:43,668
I only care about the numbers.

238
00:18:43,668 --> 00:18:45,700
Today's result is even better than I expected.

239
00:18:45,700 --> 00:18:47,616
I have nothing to say.

240
00:19:51,920 --> 00:19:53,160
He didn't answer.

241
00:19:53,160 --> 00:19:56,159
Yang, Mobai will be alright, right?

242
00:19:56,159 --> 00:19:57,984
Don't talk nonsense.

243
00:19:57,984 --> 00:19:59,499
Well, that's hard to say.

244
00:19:59,499 --> 00:20:02,179
Beautiful women's town is the hero's tomb.

245
00:20:02,179 --> 00:20:05,479
Tomb? What tomb? Shut your mouth.

246
00:20:07,359 --> 00:20:09,216
Come with me to look for him.

247
00:20:35,279 --> 00:20:37,619
You've harmed your brother.

248
00:20:38,119 --> 00:20:40,500
Don't mess with my brother anymore.

249
00:21:05,799 --> 00:21:07,512
Mr. Kuan.

250
00:21:08,039 --> 00:21:10,600
Ruifeng Battery Lab
We've been working on the Maituo battery for long.

251
00:21:10,600 --> 00:21:13,559
What if it still doesn't work this time?

252
00:21:13,559 --> 00:21:16,499
Then I should resign.

253
00:21:16,499 --> 00:21:18,268
Same.

254
00:21:18,920 --> 00:21:20,279
What do you mean?

255
00:21:20,279 --> 00:21:24,308
It means my choice is wrong.

256
